<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.2.10">
<l>tēṉārpūm puṟavil tiruviṇṇakar mēyavaṉai</l>
<l>vāṉārum matilcūḻ vayalmaṅkaiyar kōṉmaruvār</l>
<l>ūṉārvēl kaliya ṉoliceytamiḻ mālaivallār,</l>
<l>kōṉāyvā ṉavartam koṭimānakar kūṭuvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master [this] garland of Tamil [verses] composed by Kaliyaṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">whose spear is covered with the flesh of foes,</l>
<l>King of those of Maṅkai whose fields are encircled by walls which fill the sky,</l>
<l>About the one who lives in Tiruviṇṇakar in groves of nectar-filled flowers,</l>
<l>They will gather as kings in the banner [-decked] great city of the celestials.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
